Author: DavidFrumTheBlock
Text: I have wanted to buy new clothes for months but I’m terrified of my body and every time I get up the nerve to go I get into the dressing room, put on something that doesn’t fit and then get so fucking down and leave immediately.

Author: elizasbreath
Text: Personally, it took me seeking out discomfort and wearing clothes I felt really scared of while bloated before it stopped being the only thing on my mind while I was in public. It’s different for everyone unfortunately.
